# The repo's directory contents are likely generated,
# so we want to whitelist what we want to keep in git.

.env
.size-snapshot.json
.rts2*
dist

# Figma-sync intermediates: `bun run generate-src` / `generate-pictograms`
# regenerate these locally, but only the committed src/*.tsx + manifests are
# needed to build and publish. Keep the 20MB of raw SVGs and zips out of git.
icons/
*.zip
